+Date:		April, 2025
+KernelVersion:	v6.16
+Contact:	linux-coco@lists.linux.dev
+Description:
+		(RO) MRCONFIGID - 48-byte immutable storage typically used for
+		software-defined ID for non-owner-defined configuration of the
